    "body": "### Problem\n\nRunning `:che` no longer creates a new tab as the _next_ tab. Instead, it always uses the second one.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n`nvim --clean`\n`:tabnew`\n`:tabnew`\n`:che`\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nCheckhealth opens a new tab _after the current one_.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.13.0-dev-737+g02b7415324\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nN/A\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nLinux\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nfoot 1.27.0\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nAUR",
